&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;IDEO (Shanghai) is in search of a Senior Industrial Designer who will create product designs and experiences that have a genuine impact on people’s lives, can generate ideas quickly without a lot of parameters, and lead clients and teams through the industrial design phase of a project.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
