&lt;h2&gt;Senior Visual Communication Designer, Global Brand &amp;amp; Marketing, Contract-to-Hire&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;San Francisco Studio&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At IDEO, we use design to create new products, services, experiences, tangible strategies and creative capabilities.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;IDEO’s internal Global Brand &amp;amp; Marketing team is a unique place to be a designer: this work activates IDEO’s science of design with an alchemy of our wide-eyed and wonderful creative people to make futures you can click, feel, taste, test, and believe in. We ask the best questions, approach challenges with curiosity, and leverage IDEO’s 40 years of experience making audacious dreams a reality.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are in search of a Senior Visual Communication Designer who will join their fellow Global Brand &amp;amp; Marketing team members to help support IDEO’s consulting workforce of designers, futurists and dreamers. We are seeking an individual to support the team at 40 hours weekly. This is a contract-to-hire position with the potential for full-time employment based on performance and business needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;In a Nutshell:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Senior Visual Communication Designer is directly responsible for the development &amp;amp; execution of our Global Brand &amp;amp; Marketing team’s visual communications strategy.&lt;/p&gt;
