&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with multidisciplinary teams to guide project objectives and ensure alignment with team goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Utilize advanced graphic design skills to create logos, icons, symbols, and UI/visual design systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive advertising and marketing campaigns, focusing on brand storytelling and strategic possibilities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Art direct photo, video, and layout projects, ensuring high-quality visual storytelling.&lt;/li&gt;
